data.description: Charming on the outside and spacious on the inside, this home offers many amenities and updates that you don't want to miss.  Hardwood and tile floors throughout the main floor consisting of; living room, two bedrooms, updated kitchen, a full bath and main floor laundry, offer you easy clean up and one level living!  The lower level was recently finished to add a family room, 3/4 bath with tiled floors and step-in shower, a room that can easily be converted to a bedroom, a bonus room and new carpet up both flights of stairs.  The upper level was updated with new sheetrock, door, trim and recessed lighting.  Mech. updates include new furnace in 2021, new AC and smart thermostat, new water heater and new garage door opener with smart app.  Outside you will enjoy the large level lot with mature trees, large patio and new raised garden beds.  This home is conveniently located near Marion Rd. and highways 14 and 52 for a quick commute downtown and a short walk to beautiful Joyce Park.
